# ğŸŸ© PARTE 5 â€” Rollback si algo fallara

## Restaurar snapshot:

```bash
curl -X POST "http://10.10.1.4:9200/_snapshot/backup_repo/preupgrade/_restore"
```

## Downgrade:

```bash
sudo apt install elasticsearch=7.17.29
sudo apt install kibana=7.17.29
```

